Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 你筆記本掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對...對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會抹除記憶的 請不要殺我 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對有仇的人施咒的那個筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an7}（九陽：你準備蘋果了麼？）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 這是和小透的交換筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30}（九陽：果然是那種筆記麼？！）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是小透的那頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些大量的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是記憶力測試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在比賽能寫出多少至今遇到的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這記憶力好拔群啊 我是比不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到中間全是片假名的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透該不會是歸國子女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 那裡是讀過的漫畫裡的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想怎麼有奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈斯汀...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾·理夏奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱爾斯·奧古斯特·瓊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·弗朗索瓦茲·維克托瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多博奇·赫肯諾維奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗索瓦茲·普爾涅克哈克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾·波恩帕爾納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布賴恩·武科維奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷山大·加利柯森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托爾·利納迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德留斯·班狄拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉休斯·安德瑞奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩爾瓦多爾·安德列
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海賽爾·波特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉斯凱斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“有東西想給你們看 來我家”這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我第一次去小透家 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底住在怎樣的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就揭曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透住這麼好的公寓裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透真是的 不用為了收拾而先回來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有些不可告人的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡像青竹踏一樣 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}（青竹踏：竹子做的按摩腳底的工具）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別像個老婆婆一樣了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透她是個不收拾的孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都是非常地愛乾淨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄亂的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及房內側的鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是密室殺人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關開著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這不是弄髒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話 只是把垃圾箱裡的散落一片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說垃圾自己跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有長腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人類來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小倫想的應該不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亂真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子弄亂了房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這貓咪是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上撿到的 好像是被拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 貓咪是長腳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊 倫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪也可以擬人化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後會變成小透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這倒可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也跟小貓咪說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變冷了呢 小透你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 回家的路上順便去吃些什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吃點甜的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼家庭餐廳怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去商店街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店街啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼稍微繞一下遠路可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像就在這附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去買項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便貓的玩具之類的也想買一買
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話肯定有賣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有搞錯 但還是搞錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:53.04,*Default,+.,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}成人玩具店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是白色的貓 什麼顏色比較配呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色？還是藍色？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼的認真 你很看重那只小貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很看重小倫喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到G·N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 請那邊入座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 請坐在沙發側
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是小倫去坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起坐就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 關於我家的小貓啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪一種飲料真難決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放了幾種飲料在裡面啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次放入了5種美味的混合飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓的名字還沒有決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心或者果汁的名字怎麼樣？小透和很喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個想法不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在放在這裡面的有 可樂 蘇打 彈珠汽水 薑汁汽水 哈密瓜汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部合在一起就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還精神嗎？從今天開始你的名字就叫碳酸了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很乖巧呢 這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會鬧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸 項圈很適合你喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要吃飯了嗎？現在就給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 碳酸的玩具我們也買來了 吃完飯後一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 我們來聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果小倫一直被搶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經那麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 制服上會粘毛上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間陪你玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從早上開始就是相當寒冷的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午開始下雪的可能性會較高 出門的時候請多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像會下雪哦 小倫 雖然只是預報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把醬汁拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來蘸雪吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 今天從早上開始就很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 怎麼回事啊 那身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽天氣預報說會下雪 為此的對策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像暗殺者一樣 很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和變態搞錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼這麼冷還非要來學校不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所當然的 因為是學生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天結束後 直到春天為止都放寒假不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天 很討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的時候你也一直說好熱 好熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再下雪的話我都沒有自信活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛一臉苦悶啊 下雪盡是高興的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以堆雪人 做雪屋 打雪仗 所以小凪也來祈禱下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有聽我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:00.02,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,118)}{\fad(0,300)}第一節課
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.32,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,118)}{\fad(300,300)}第二節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.91,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,118)}{\fad(300,300)}第三節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.37,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,118)}{\fad(300,300)}第四節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都...不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已經放棄一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 天氣真是說變就變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 午飯午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起雪你還是吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雪看來會集起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想在厚厚的雪裡這樣做一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋的深到看不到底的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像漫畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡跳下去能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個應該...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那從屋頂跳下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集起來了~ 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小倫 死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 大家也跳進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然做什麼呢 很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子擺了奇怪的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪真是溫暖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們讓凪暖和起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 小倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了凪在做雪屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那樣會很溫暖呢 我要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 暖和了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是比外面好一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子有破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
